                     <note>
                        <p>Translation and commentary on the <title>Usūl al-Kāfī</title> of the great scholar of Shīʿī fiqh, <persName key="viaf_60393215" role="ant">ʿAllāmah Kulaynī</persName> or <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="viaf_60393215" ref="https://lccn.loc.gov/n80158377" role="ant">Abū Jaʿfar Muḥammad ibn Yaʿqūb ibn Isḥāq al-Rāzī al-Kulaynī</persName>, entitled <title>Ṣāfī</title> (written <title>Shāfī</title>), by <persName key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164656394.0x000001 viaf_1632455" role="aut">Khalīl ibn al-Ghāzī al-Qazvīnī</persName> (1001-1089/1593-1678), written in Shaʿbān 1064/June 1654 at the order of <persName key="viaf_268954445" role="pat">Shāh ʿAbbās II Ṣafavī</persName>
                        </p>
                        <p>Defective at end </p>
                        <p>Not dated 
</p>
                        <p>Unbound; loose folios; boards of binding delaminating </p>
                        <p>Inscribed and seal impressed by later donor of vaqf at beginning: <persName key="person_f7343" role="fmo">Muḥammad Bāqir ibn Muḥammad Riz̤āʾ</persName>
                        </p>
